obsidian_action_tab_goto_4                     C-4
obsidian_action_tab_goto_5                     C-5
obsidian_action_tab_goto_6                     C-6
obsidian_action_tab_goto_7                     C-7
obsidian_action_tab_goto_8                     C-8
obsidian_action_tab_goto_last                  C-9

