obsidian_action_pane_left                      A-left
obsidian_action_pane_right                     A-right
obsidian_action_pane_above                     A-up
obsidian_action_pane_below                     A-down
obsidian_action_pane_toggle                    A-q
obsidian_action_pane_max                       (macro A-s A-S-s)
