obsidian_action_!new                           C-A-S-n
obsidian_action_!!new                          C-A-s
obsidian_action_open                           right
obsidian_action_parent                         left
obsidian_action_view                           (macro C-A-p S-o p e n spc w i t h spc S-c h r o m e)
